    "To address this, Malone et al. (2023) presented a custom grading system for Jupyter notebooks integrated into a gamified learning platform for a cybersecurity course.",
    "The system focusses on design, feedback, and security, allowing students to exploit vulnerabilities while protecting the system.",
    "Tabletop exercises represent a pioneering instructional approach applied in real-world scenarios to train teams to respond to incidents and evaluate emergency plans (Švábenský et al., 2024).",
    "Exercise Platform (IXP) supports such an innovative approach by introducing a web-based tool designed to perform and evaluate these exercises.",
    "Unlike traditional methods, IXP automates the analysis of student interaction data, improving evaluation, and offering insights into student learning."
